{"tid":498384,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"想買即影即有送比女友 有無介紹","createTime":"2017-12-13T17:31:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T09:50:44.000Z","uid":162061,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"17661f99c45079a26ef1366ce718da3660b5caaf","tid":498384,"uid":162061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:31:49.000Z","msg":"小弟同女朋友 2個平時都無玩開相機 相關知識係接近0<br />\n但係因為拍拖始終都想影下相 留下紀念咁 <br />\n所以想買部即影即有<br />\n<br />\n小弟近排睇到款 kodak ms210 唔知有無師兄有用過？<br />\n係上網睇好似相紙比其他牌子既貴<br />\n或者有無其他抵玩d？<br />\n<br />\n其實價錢貴少少唔係問題，只係驚買左唔岩玩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739cf972bf4ca131716268a53f297e3c934fac8c","tid":498384,"uid":36157,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:43:31.000Z","msg":"我睇完你個原因<br />\n<br />\n既然無限金錢又唔識影<br />\n我提議你買部無反<br />\n或者宜家女女流行嘅自拍機<br />\n<br />\n如果你確實係0攝影認識<br />\n即影即有我覺得係唔岩你<br />\n<br />\n勉強只會不斷嘥錢<br />\n而且影唔到值得保留嘅野"},{"pid":"5d0a45f00e5dd5dc0e96ff137c797016b464f2cf","tid":498384,"uid":80740,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:45:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我睇完你個原因<br />\n<br />\n既然無限金錢又唔識影<br />\n我提議你買部無反<br />\n或者宜家女女流行嘅自拍機<br />\n<br />\n如果你確實係0攝影認識<br />\n即影即有我覺得係唔岩你<br />\n<br />\n勉強只會不斷嘥錢<br />\n而且影唔到值得保留嘅野</blockquote><br />\n痴線即影即有中學生都識影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最多咪叫條女影"},{"pid":"c4213993ed6a92c8b1ecdcab29b2160c438e9162","tid":498384,"uid":10023,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:45:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我睇完你個原因<br />\n<br />\n既然無限金錢又唔識影<br />\n我提議你買部無反<br />\n或者宜家女女流行嘅自拍機<br />\n<br />\n如果你確實係0攝影認識<br />\n即影即有我覺得係唔岩你<br />\n<br />\n勉強只會不斷嘥錢<br />\n而且影唔到值得保留嘅野</blockquote><br />\n買部printer咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手機影 printer印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b7ae15405ff76ed59d15bc9a524ee8f5b2b0d4","tid":498384,"uid":90128,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:50:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我睇完你個原因<br />\n<br />\n既然無限金錢又唔識影<br />\n我提議你買部無反<br />\n或者宜家女女流行嘅自拍機<br />\n<br />\n如果你確實係0攝影認識<br />\n即影即有我覺得係唔岩你<br />\n<br />\n勉強只會不斷嘥錢<br />\n而且影唔到值得保留嘅野</blockquote><br />\n買部printer咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手機影 printer印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n推printer<br />\n即影即有好難搞 <br />\n自拍又難就角度<br />\n有時一係太光一係太暗<br />\n想影張靚又要用半盒相紙"},{"pid":"35a7cd829c83de69d08de76730243ff8b24d259f","tid":498384,"uid":162061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:53:58.000Z","msg":"巴打講得都有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n始終無掂過即影即有 都有諗過哂相紙呢d問題<br />\n<br />\n但係始終都係想學下 玩下 <br />\n當第一次試下咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n至於買printer呢個提議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係無諗過&hellip;"},{"pid":"46bac08772128319dded40418d59a4d844d38faa","tid":498384,"uid":36157,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:55:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我睇完你個原因<br />\n<br />\n既然無限金錢又唔識影<br />\n我提議你買部無反<br />\n或者宜家女女流行嘅自拍機<br />\n<br />\n如果你確實係0攝影認識<br />\n即影即有我覺得係唔岩你<br />\n<br />\n勉強只會不斷嘥錢<br />\n而且影唔到值得保留嘅野</blockquote><br />\n買部printer咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手機影 printer印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n推printer<br />\n即影即有好難搞 <br />\n自拍又難就角度<br />\n有時一係太光一係太暗<br />\n想影張靚又要用半盒相紙</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係好難搞姐。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我都試過只係個lighten/darken都解釋10分鐘，對方雖然最後話明但其實我覺得對方只係驚問太多。<br />\n<br />\n只係唔知道樓主攝影有幾接近0 <br />\n不過無限金錢其實科技可以搭夠嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ebfb607f8e2d090d4ae7c02de0e622ad98e7a3","tid":498384,"uid":162061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:56:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我睇完你個原因<br />\n<br />\n既然無限金錢又唔識影<br />\n我提議你買部無反<br />\n或者宜家女女流行嘅自拍機<br />\n<br />\n如果你確實係0攝影認識<br />\n即影即有我覺得係唔岩你<br />\n<br />\n勉強只會不斷嘥錢<br />\n而且影唔到值得保留嘅野</blockquote><br />\n我其實都有諗過市面上d 自拍神器<br />\n但係我就倒番轉諗 因為依家都用電話app影相 <br />\n加埋p埋圖咁 自拍神器 好似同依家d影相app無分別咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 都多謝巴打既意見先"},{"pid":"ffa12dc02542b466e1e7daa353bb337c0c657bf4","tid":498384,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:59:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打講得都有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n始終無掂過即影即有 都有諗過哂相紙呢d問題<br />\n<br />\n但係始終都係想學下 玩下 <br />\n當第一次試下咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n至於買printer呢個提議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係無諗過&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n一係咁<br />\n如果你又想同女友有留影<br />\n自拍？當女友係model咁影？<br />\n<br />\n將你嘅錢分兩部分<br />\n<br />\n一部無反/自拍機：保證有成功嘅相<br />\n一架即影即有：學上面巴打話齋都唔係太難，不過要同時影哂你兩個就可能要第三人幫手影。"},{"pid":"4f560220e37ae3e31a84063d5eccac00783873aa","tid":498384,"uid":162061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T18:01:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我睇完你個原因<br />\n<br />\n既然無限金錢又唔識影<br />\n我提議你買部無反<br />\n或者宜家女女流行嘅自拍機<br />\n<br />\n如果你確實係0攝影認識<br />\n即影即有我覺得係唔岩你<br />\n<br />\n勉強只會不斷嘥錢<br />\n而且影唔到值得保留嘅野</blockquote><br />\n買部printer咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手機影 printer印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n推printer<br />\n即影即有好難搞 <br />\n自拍又難就角度<br />\n有時一係太光一係太暗<br />\n想影張靚又要用半盒相紙</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係好難搞姐。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我都試過只係個lighten/darken都解釋10分鐘，對方雖然最後話明但其實我覺得對方只係驚問太多。<br />\n<br />\n只係唔知道樓主攝影有幾接近0 <br />\n不過無限金錢其實科技可以搭夠嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實攝影技巧都叫有d掛&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n但係你話講到調教曝光呀 較光圈用咩鏡頭果d 真係真係唔係太認識<br />\n（之前有個fd教過我 都係一知半解，叫做知道有咩用 係咩黎咁）<br />\n<br />\n正正因為唔係話太好攝影 所以想追求部對我黎講比較&ldquo;簡單&ldquo;既機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n但係我無諗過原來即影即有都好似咁難搞咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d63f6871f8d254d8b51ff6c40f4b8ac08fdf74","tid":498384,"uid":162061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T18:03:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打講得都有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n始終無掂過即影即有 都有諗過哂相紙呢d問題<br />\n<br />\n但係始終都係想學下 玩下 <br />\n當第一次試下咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n至於買printer呢個提議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係無諗過&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n一係咁<br />\n如果你又想同女友有留影<br />\n自拍？當女友係model咁影？<br />\n<br />\n將你嘅錢分兩部分<br />\n<br />\n一部無反/自拍機：保證有成功嘅相<br />\n一架即影即有：學上面巴打話齋都唔係太難，不過要同時影哂你兩個就可能要第三人幫手影。</blockquote><br />\n我諗自拍／影佢都會有 <br />\n其實真係買一部相機都有諗過 但因為始終都未有時間學 <br />\n同埋價錢上 依家對我黎講即影即有相對比較平 都係原因之一"},{"pid":"cd26d507398149fa8d0bc31011c246f0d6d1cd97","tid":498384,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T18:05:42.000Z","msg":"Spectra. 輕過SX70又全自動"},{"pid":"612900bc455e28d7c27ec350aab4ff743f199f02","tid":498384,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T18:07:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n我諗自拍／影佢都會有 <br />\n其實真係買一部相機都有諗過 但因為始終都未有時間學 <br />\n同埋價錢上 依家對我黎講即影即有相對比較平 都係原因之一</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁無反都唔係架架貴<br />\n影相從來都係平有平玩豐儉由人嘅姐<br />\n<br />\n起碼一拎上手影 你都即刻有渣拿"},{"pid":"faf1b77418fa569bf0528bfa54e0c56cb0b36829","tid":498384,"uid":147770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T18:09:38.000Z","msg":"既影既有先講技術"},{"pid":"cb7590b2dd695830cb27814d675c0a75cb75b44e","tid":498384,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T18:11:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>既影既有先講技術</blockquote><br />\n人地燒電練，即影即有燒錢練技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cefbdcb50a3dc0332609530aac840a94fee531e6","tid":498384,"uid":48687,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T18:14:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/021135_fe6186c40535e6b6615526c51a270367.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F021135_fe6186c40535e6b6615526c51a270367.jpg&h=15954e67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個得唔得？<br />\n咁啱我女朋友今日話我知買左部 cap左圖<br />\n$370-400一部<br />\n用平時即影即有機相紙"},{"pid":"be09a3c6d2f73e716981f938d8a1fe85f1d9206a","tid":498384,"uid":48687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T18:16:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n呢個得唔得？<br />\n咁啱我女朋友今日話我知買左部 cap左圖<br />\n$370-400一部<br />\n用平時即影即有機相紙</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢買呢部野原因係...拎去旅行比人揸機啲人影唔到<br />\n覺得浪費相紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"219b543251265e1a4143854f049042012e44f30b","tid":498384,"uid":69447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T18:41:01.000Z","msg":"其實printer真係比較好 <br />\n佢想執相 可以手機自拍完執完就print得<br />\n唔需要晒相紙試<br />\n一齊執下整下相都sweet d啦<br />\nGathering時share部機同frd一齊玩又得<br />\n<br />\n至於相機 如果買 我諗用prosumer機仔起步較好<br />\n依家好多都有反mon 輕便又有畫質 旅行又用得<br />\n不過個價梗係高一截 1吋sensor機$3k-6k都有 睇你需要"},{"pid":"fd9d4e810585086b337eb3c2e882fe4c53c73c0b","tid":498384,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T22:59:19.000Z","msg":"fujifilm instax sp3, 咩來自己google 吓；<br />\n已經買咗部準備做聖誕禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb16d11ce26e8617d808f47033426fd89f4fc18","tid":498384,"uid":83426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T23:42:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8abf9e5e7b7f45c19e287f3bb7470b666d41957d","tid":498384,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T01:09:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實printer真係比較好 <br />\n佢想執相 可以手機自拍完執完就print得<br />\n唔需要晒相紙試<br />\n一齊執下整下相都sweet d啦<br />\nGathering時share部機同frd一齊玩又得<br />\n<br />\n至於相機 如果買 我諗用prosumer機仔起步較好<br />\n依家好多都有反mon 輕便又有畫質 旅行又用得<br />\n不過個價梗係高一截 1吋sensor機$3k-6k都有 睇你需要</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用返iphone影去印都冇得輸"},{"pid":"2739e5367828948e2b6ed7a5c14139b2b4e73aa6","tid":498384,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T01:18:47.000Z","msg":"近牌睇中左部OneStep2"},{"pid":"0484ca0d8ec7e32faec8ca0f59f4cab3fb26e16b","tid":498384,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T01:29:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>近牌睇中左部OneStep2</blockquote><br />\none step都幾大部,摺唔埋呢下好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427e37d125a00586ae0eb7561185495f558bf1aa","tid":498384,"uid":35045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T01:30:31.000Z","msg":"Polaroid 180 <br />\n玩完返唔到轉頭"},{"pid":"92da7dfabe1c27b0ee841236da9f5a894798a086","tid":498384,"uid":104247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T02:44:46.000Z","msg":"送俾女友<br />\n一於富賤 mini 系列 囉<br />\n全自動，冇嘢set , 零 fail"}]}